1 You are provided with a Movie class, a StreamingPlatform class and a Tester class with the Main method,

a) The Streaming Platform wants to add a new kind of Entertainment to their collection: TV Shows. TV Shows have a Director, Genre and numEpisodes.
Implement this class and modify the starter code so that the StreamingPlatform class can keep track of both TV Shows and Movies in its collection. Follow good design principles.

b) Using the Strategy design pattern, create a method findEntertainment in the StreamingPlatform class to find Entertainment by Director or by Genre
Demonstrate the usage in the Tester class with suitable examples.

2
 a) Make it so that only one instance of the StreamingPlatform can be created. Use an appropriate design pattern.

b) Draw a UML diagram of your code from questions 1 and 2
